1
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,280
Get in.

2
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,079
What are you doing? Don't move! What are you doing?

3
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,079
What are you doing?

4
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:51,560
Don't move.

5
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,480
What are you guys doing?

6
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,560
Is this how the police arrest people?

7
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:00,719
Move, move, move. Get over there.

8
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,599
Get up, get up! What are you doing?

9
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,400
What do you mean "what are we doing"? You know exactly why.

10
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:04,680
I'm just waiting for a ride here.

11
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,799
You—you must have the wrong person.

12
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,159
I'm telling you, cooperate.

13
00:02:07,359 --> 00:02:08,039
Cooperating is one thing.

14
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,599
Not cooperating is a whole different matter.

15
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,080
I'm telling you, you've got the wrong person.

16
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,479
Let me tell you something.

17
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:12,360
Think carefully about it yourself.

18
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:12,919
Which is better, which is worse?

19
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:13,960
I'm not going to waste words with you.

20
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,879
Open the car window.

21
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,520
Come on, take a look.

22
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:31,280
You understand it clearly this time, right?

23
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,360
Do you know that person just now?

24
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,199
No, I don't.

25
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,280
Alright, I'll tell you.

26
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,479
His name is Ge Xiaohui.

27
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:52,120
He knows you.

28
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:55,159
He said An Pinghai sent him to deliver goods to you.

29
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:59,159
An who? I don't know him either.

30
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,800
Huang Xin, let me be clear with you.

31
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,719
Whether you admit it now or not,

32
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:04,639
or whether you cooperate or not,

33
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:06,199
it doesn't matter to us anymore.

34
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,680
Ge Xiaohui is cooperating with us now.

35
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:11,240
An Pinghai is already our target.

36
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,560
We'll arrest him sooner or later.

37
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:14,120
Do you think he can get away?

38
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,560
I'm giving you a chance right now.

39
00:03:17,199 --> 00:03:18,360
If you cooperate,

40
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,960
just tell An Pinghai the goods have been received.

41
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,159
If you don't cooperate,

42
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:24,000
we'll take you away right now.

43
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,479
Are you taking it or not?

44
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,199
I'm asking you one last time.

45
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,479
Are you taking it or not?

46
00:03:38,319 --> 00:03:39,120
I'll take it.

47
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,800
Speak properly.

48
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:43,520
If you mess this up, it's all on you.

49
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,280
Do you understand?

50
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,560
Hello?

51
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,000
What took you so long?

52
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,879
I was in the bathroom and didn't hear.

53
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,919
I got the stuff, it went pretty smoothly.

54
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,520
Next time, even if you're peeing, you have to answer my call.

55
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,319
I checked the number. It's useless.

56
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,519
How are things on An Pinghai's side?

57
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:33,480
Has his suspicion been cleared?

58
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,360
Hard to say.

59
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:37,879
I think he'll look for Ge Xiaohui again soon.

60
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,600
He'll have him deliver goods to Zhang Shengli.

61
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,639
First, to test him further.

62
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,680
Second, to prepare for his next move.

63
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,399
Hurry and bring Zhang Shengli over too.

64
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,279
Make sure nothing goes wrong.

65
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,000
Understood.

66
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:14,639
Old Ge

67
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,199
Don't move, don't move.

68
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:21,680
Who is it?

69
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,360
Don't move.

70
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,000
Get up, get up.

71
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,800
What's going on?

72
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:25,319
What are you doing?

73
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:26,199
Why are you shouting?

74
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:27,360
What are you doing?

75
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:28,240
Master

76
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:28,920
What's your name?

77
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:30,920
What's your name?

78
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,920
Zhang Shengli

79
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,439
It's you. Come, take him away.

80
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:34,120
Go, go.

81
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,399
Take it back.

82
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,959
Don't move. Don't move.

83
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,519
Still not talking, huh?

84
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:53,079
Don't pretend to be mute here.

85
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:54,079
I'm telling you,

86
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:55,360
we know everything that's going on.

87
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,120
Do you understand?

88
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,759
You can choose not to cooperate with us.

89
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:59,079
But that won't stop me from handing you over to the authorities.

90
00:05:59,079 --> 00:05:59,800
Do you get it?

91
00:06:00,079 --> 00:06:01,000
But if you're smart,

92
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,120
you'll choose to help us catch An Pinghai.

93
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,680
When the judge sentences you,

94
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,800
we can choose to help you get a lighter sentence.

95
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,600
Do you understand?

96
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:09,160
Although in every stage of An Pinghai's drug trafficking operation

97
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,720
each of you had your own responsibilities,

98
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,519
there are still main offenders and accomplices.

99
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,319
Our main target is An Pinghai,

100
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,519
not a small-time player like you.

101
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,639
Think about it yourself.

102
00:06:20,439 --> 00:06:21,319
Are you still trying to hold out?

103
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,160
Do you know how we caught you?

104
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,560
I'll be honest with you.

105
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:26,399
We've already arrested Ge Xiaohui.

106
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,959
He’s cooperating with us now.

107
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:28,879
Impossible.

108
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,240
That guy’s a bigger deal than me.

109
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,480
Loosen up, will you? Don’t move.

110
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,360
I can’t run. Don’t move.

111
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,120
The more you move, the tighter it gets.

112
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:33,959
I can’t run.

113
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:35,000
Where do you think you are?

114
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:38,839
Do you know someone with the last name Huang?

115
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,600
Who? Huang Xin?

116
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,519
Arresting you, arresting those two,

117
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,439
it’s all to catch An Pinghai.

118
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,959
Let me tell you,

119
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,000
An Pinghai might call you soon.

120
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,000
If you cooperate, it’ll count as a merit for you.

121
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,560
If you don’t cooperate,

122
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,759
we’ll catch An Pinghai sooner or later anyway.

123
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:55,079
Because those two have already cooperated.

124
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,959
I’m giving you a chance now.

125
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,959
It’s up to you whether you seize it.

126
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,959
Do you hear me?

127
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,120
We’re definitely going to catch An Pinghai.

128
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,920
It’s just a matter of time.

129
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:10,959
If it’s sooner, you can get leniency.

130
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:12,920
If it’s later, you’ll both go down together.

131
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:20,199
Have you made up your mind?

132
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,519
I'm asking you one last time—have you decided?

133
00:07:25,079 --> 00:07:27,079
Hello, we've got the goods.

134
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:29,720
We can't take these three back yet.

135
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,000
An Pinghai could contact them at any time.

136
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,480
He might call them to get in touch.

137
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:33,560
I suggest

138
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,639
we temporarily detain these three at the hotel.

139
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,720
Just in case.

140
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,920
Yes.

141
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,240
Understood.

142
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,519
Master.

143
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:10,439
Master, um, Master—

144
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:12,959
Can I go wash my hair?

145
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:15,680
Forget it.

146
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,720
My head itches.

147
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:25,720
An Pinghai could contact you again at any time.

148
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,720
I know what to say.

149
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,919
Xia Yu, the food is here. Let's eat first.

150
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:46,440
Thank you.

151
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,120
No problem.

152
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:49,960
Come on.

153
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,279
Master, let me add this for you.

154
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,200
Isn't there rice? Why make instant noodles?

155
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:06,480
Longevity noodles—instant noodles count as longevity noodles too.

156
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:07,600
Happy birthday.

157
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,519
I was wondering why your shimu called me.

158
00:09:11,799 --> 00:09:12,720
Happy birthday.

159
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:13,720
Stop messing around.

160
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,039
Let's eat.

161
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,879
Nothing good here.

162
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:24,559
Let's just make do with this.

163
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,879
Once we catch An Pinghai and get back to the station,

164
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,720
I'll pay to get you something better.

165
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:37,080
Can I have a pair of chopsticks?

166
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,200
How about I feed you?

167
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:42,399
Didn't school teach you what a criminal suspect is?

168
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,559
Chopsticks won't work.

169
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,559
Let's just make do with a spoon.

170
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,080
Bring some noodles.

171
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:08,360
Eat some more.

172
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,399
I'll have to trouble you again in a bit.

173
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,679
After you finish eating, get a good rest.

174
00:10:13,399 --> 00:10:13,960
Thank you.

175
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:19,559
Are you two having noodles?

176
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,799
Give me some, too.

177
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,799
That's enough, just leave me some soup.

178
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,039
Master

179
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:50,080
Get ready.

180
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,679
I'll be back soon.

181
00:10:52,159 --> 00:10:53,519
This time, I hit the jackpot.

182
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,679
Okay, Brother Hai.

183
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,840
Then when you come back, we'll throw you a welcome party.

184
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:58,639
No need, let's keep it low-key.

185
00:10:59,879 --> 00:11:00,960
I don't even know what's going on.

186
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:03,360
My right eyelid has been twitching a lot these past couple of days.

187
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,519
Maybe you're just happy.

188
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:10,519
No, I have a bad feeling about it.

189
00:11:11,519 --> 00:11:12,639
It's fine, um...

190
00:11:12,759 --> 00:11:15,039
I'll go to the Dragon King Temple and burn two sticks of incense for you.

191
00:11:15,399 --> 00:11:16,279
They say it's really effective there.

192
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:20,080
Alright, wait for my call for the details.

193
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:21,360
Okay.

194
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,360
Not bad.

195
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,320
Officer Liu

196
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:33,000
When you arrest Lao An this time,

197
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,480
you need to be careful.

198
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:39,639
Why?

199
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:42,879
Actually, before he left this time,

200
00:11:44,639 --> 00:11:46,279
he was always suspicious and paranoid.

201
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:47,799
He was constantly uneasy.

202
00:11:48,919 --> 00:11:52,080
He didn't just go back to his hometown to deliver goods this time.

203
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,000
He also went to get some weapons.

204
00:11:55,919 --> 00:11:56,720
Really?

205
00:12:01,799 --> 00:12:02,799
He's pretty ruthless.

206
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,639
Yesterday, he kept ordering me around.

207
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,799
That shows he's become even more suspicious.

208
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:10,000
So this time when he comes back,

209
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:11,600
he'll definitely be carrying a weapon.

210
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:12,440
If you try to catch him,

211
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,799
he'll fight to the death for sure.

212
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:41,639
He's not that skinny, he should be a bit fatter.

213
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,759
And his mouth should be a bit bigger.

214
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:14,919
Go to the hotel and book me a new room.

215
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,159
On a different floor.

216
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:17,519
Okay.

217
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,559
That's about right.

218
00:13:57,759 --> 00:13:58,559
Hello

219
00:13:58,679 --> 00:13:59,679
Get me a car rental.

220
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:01,720
What kind of car do you want?

221
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:04,159
I'll give you a number. You'll know when you get there.

222
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:05,919
So where should I deliver the car?

223
00:14:05,919 --> 00:14:07,600
Just keep it for now and wait for my call.

224
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,000
Wait, you—

225
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:13,840
Ziming, hurry over here.

226
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,320
Our people are all around.

227
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,120
Don't get any ideas.

228
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,720
Don't make trouble for yourself.

229
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,519
I'll give you at most two minutes.

230
00:14:23,879 --> 00:14:25,519
Get the key and come out immediately.

231
00:14:25,759 --> 00:14:26,759
Do you understand?

232
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:28,720
Understood.

233
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,559
Captain Liu, things have come to this.

234
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:32,600
Of course I'll cooperate.

235
00:14:46,799 --> 00:14:47,559
It's too tight.

236
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,039
Wait a moment.

237
00:14:54,679 --> 00:14:55,759
Put this on first.

238
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:02,039
I'll loosen the cuffs for you when I get back.

239
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:03,639
Thanks.

240
00:17:24,559 --> 00:17:25,359
Captain Huang

241
00:17:25,799 --> 00:17:27,079
An Pinghai just called.

242
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:28,640
He said that after 7 p.m. tonight, Ge Xiaohui

243
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,200
shouldn't go anywhere.

244
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,359
He should stay in his room.

245
00:17:31,519 --> 00:17:32,319
Okay.

246
00:17:35,079 --> 00:17:35,960
What about Zhang Shengli?

247
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:36,759
No movement.

248
00:17:37,079 --> 00:17:37,880
Here's what you do.

249
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,240
Go back and keep a close eye on him.

250
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,480
I'll report to the bureau now.

251
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,039
We'll try to take him down as soon as he enters the lobby.

252
00:17:42,039 --> 00:17:42,759
Understood.

253
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:07,799
Welcome.

254
00:18:19,079 --> 00:18:20,160
All spotters, stay alert.

255
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:22,279
Pay special attention to entrances and exits, especially those with stairs.

256
00:18:22,279 --> 00:18:23,160
Keep a close watch for me.

257
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:24,680
Welcome.

258
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:28,720
Master.

259
00:18:29,319 --> 00:18:30,480
Once this case is closed,

260
00:18:30,599 --> 00:18:32,039
We should have a good meal together.

261
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,839
All you ever think about is eating.

262
00:18:35,319 --> 00:18:36,799
Once we finish our task later,

263
00:18:36,799 --> 00:18:38,519
Master has to hurry back.

264
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:41,039
He can still celebrate his wife's birthday, right?

265
00:18:41,279 --> 00:18:42,039
That's true.

266
00:18:42,279 --> 00:18:43,759
We really should have a good meal.

267
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:47,480
Otherwise, there won't even be energy left to kneel on the washboard at home.

268
00:19:12,039 --> 00:19:14,519
Manager, what is this place?

269
00:19:14,599 --> 00:19:15,519
The heat pump room.

270
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,519
Can someone get in there?

271
00:19:19,039 --> 00:19:20,079
It's possible.

272
00:19:21,119 --> 00:19:22,160
Zhao Dali, Zhao Dali.

273
00:19:22,319 --> 00:19:23,119
Quick, send two people.

274
00:19:23,119 --> 00:19:24,640
Go take a look at that heat pump room.

275
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,240
Don't get exposed.

276
00:19:25,240 --> 00:19:26,160
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

