00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:50,639
Isn't your brother-in-law really rich?

554
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:52,119
He's in rehab.

555
00:35:52,519 --> 00:35:54,079
I forgot, drugs.

556
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:55,679
Right, right, right.

557
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:58,079
What about that senior guy?

558
00:35:58,480 --> 00:36:00,199
His business is doing great now.

559
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:02,079
As soon as Lei heard I wanted to buy a house,

560
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:05,079
he transferred the money to me without hesitation.

561
00:36:06,159 --> 00:36:07,480
Is it inconvenient for you?

562
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:08,679
If it's inconvenient, just forget it.

563
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:11,000
Don't get upset.

564
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:12,719
How much are you short?

565
00:36:12,719 --> 00:36:13,480
Fifty thousand.

566
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:16,320
There's nothing left from Tingting either.

567
00:36:17,039 --> 00:36:18,800
I haven't told Tingting about this.

568
00:36:18,800 --> 00:36:19,679
She doesn't know.

569
00:36:20,039 --> 00:36:22,239
I want to tell her when we get the house.

570
00:36:22,639 --> 00:36:24,000
Good, that's good.

571
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,039
Give her a surprise.

572
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:26,639
Well, um...

573
00:36:27,000 --> 00:36:29,679
There's nothing I can do with my in-laws either.

574
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:31,119
Alright, alright.

575
00:36:32,599 --> 00:36:33,599
Send me your bank account number.

576
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:39,360
I knew you had some secret savings.

577
00:36:40,199 --> 00:36:42,039
Don't tell your wife about this.

578
00:36:42,039 --> 00:36:43,639
Don't worry, I won't see her.

579
00:36:47,599 --> 00:36:48,440
It's over now.

580
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,920
This afternoon, I'll transfer it this afternoon.

581
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:54,199
Don't worry, Brother Yang.

582
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:55,880
I'll pay it back monthly.

583
00:36:56,079 --> 00:36:57,320
Every month, as soon as I get my salary,

584
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:58,880
I'll give it to you first, okay?

585
00:36:59,239 --> 00:37:00,800
No rush, no rush.

586
00:37:01,079 --> 00:37:03,440
Um, why don't you ask Master to lend you some more?

587
00:37:03,639 --> 00:37:05,679
Master? I wouldn't dare.

588
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:06,519
Besides, he's not here.

589
00:37:06,519 --> 00:37:07,400
I just went to look for him.

590
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,800
It seems he went out of town.

591
00:37:09,079 --> 00:37:09,880
I'm leaving now.

592
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,800
Alright, no rush to pay it back.

593
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:13,400
I know, I know there's no rush.

594
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,679
No rush.

595
00:37:16,679 --> 00:37:17,679
No rush, really.

596
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:23,519
Who is it?

597
00:37:24,599 --> 00:37:25,159
It's me.

598
00:37:29,599 --> 00:37:30,000
Sis.

599
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:30,639
I'm here.

600
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,679
Don't move, let me do it.

601
00:37:36,639 --> 00:37:37,480
Where's Nizi?

602
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:40,000
She went to kindergarten.

603
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,920
What's wrong? Are you not feeling well?

604
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:47,519
I'm feeling a bit unwell.

605
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,440
That day, I...

606
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,960
I spoke a bit harshly.

607
00:37:55,039 --> 00:37:56,079
Don't be mad, okay?

608
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:03,400
I came to tell you

609
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:06,320
there's closed-off management at my brother-in-law's place.

610
00:38:06,519 --> 00:38:07,519
The conditions are pretty good.

611
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:09,159
There's plenty of food and drink.

612
00:38:11,039 --> 00:38:11,920
If things go quickly,

613
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,679
you could be out in about three months.

614
00:38:16,599 --> 00:38:18,760
Maybe by then you'll have quit smoking, too.

615
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:20,000
And quit drinking as well.

616
00:38:20,719 --> 00:38:21,760
Isn't that a good thing?

617
00:38:25,239 --> 00:38:27,039
Alright, I got it.

618
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:29,199
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

619
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:30,480
I'll go get you something to eat.

620
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:31,679
Don't bother.

621
00:38:32,239 --> 00:38:33,960
I just came to see you for a moment.

622
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,320
Tingting is still waiting for me.

623
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:36,519
I need to go back and take care of her.

624
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,480
You haven't even had any water.

625
00:38:38,719 --> 00:38:39,559
I'll take a sip.

626
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,199
Don't be upset.

627
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:44,360
I'm not upset, why would I be?

628
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,719
If you're not feeling well, take some medicine.

629
00:38:45,719 --> 00:38:46,559
Alright, alright.

630
00:38:48,840 --> 00:38:49,480
Okay.

631
00:38:50,039 --> 00:38:50,719
I'm leaving now. Go on.

632
00:38:50,719 --> 00:38:51,760
I won't see you out.

633
00:39:19,159 --> 00:39:19,880
Get in the car.

634
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:25,079
You really made me your driver, huh?

635
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:31,000
Unbelievable.

636
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:34,039
You even brought your own relatives in.

637
00:39:34,239 --> 00:39:36,239
Only you would do something like this.

638
00:39:39,079 --> 00:39:40,039
I've thought it through.

639
00:39:40,039 --> 00:39:41,079
I don't blame you.

640
00:39:55,599 --> 00:39:56,840
Why are we stopping here?

641
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,199
Where are you going?

642
00:40:00,320 --> 00:40:01,280
I'm going to take a walk.

643
00:40:02,159 --> 00:40:03,559
There's a restroom over there.

644
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:09,760
Why did you come all the way here?

645
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:15,440
I want to go to the bathroom.

646
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:42,239
Every day you act like you're sick or something.

647
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:45,519
You made Vasily like this.

648
00:40:46,199 --> 00:40:47,119
Impressive.

649
00:40:47,639 --> 00:40:49,239
Why do you keep coming here for no reason?

650
00:40:52,800 --> 00:40:53,480
Wait a minute.

651
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:12,719
Speak properly.

652
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,920
I have something to do, so I'll head back first.

653
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:17,559
Call me if you need anything.

654
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:18,559
Okay.

655
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:36,239
You're back. Go take a shower quickly.

656
00:41:37,000 --> 00:41:37,840
Dinner will be ready soon.

657
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:38,840
There are still two more dishes.

658
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:41,199
Ni Zi, Daddy's home.

659
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:45,719
Dad!

660
00:41:47,599 --> 00:41:48,239
Come here!

661
00:41:50,239 --> 00:41:51,679
Let me take a look at you.

662
00:41:53,760 --> 00:41:54,559
You've gotten heavier.

663
00:41:55,639 --> 00:41:57,239
Daddy, you're finally back!

664
00:41:57,239 --> 00:41:59,079
Take me out to play for a while, please.

665
00:41:59,079 --> 00:41:59,760
Where do you want to go?

666
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:01,440
No, you can't go out to play.

667
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:02,239
You only have to learn six words.

668
00:42:02,239 --> 00:42:03,079
You haven't learned them yet.

669
00:42:03,079 --> 00:42:04,400
Let Daddy teach you.

670
00:42:04,519 --> 00:42:06,039
You can play after you finish learning.

671
00:42:07,119 --> 00:42:07,599
Oh no.

672
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:08,880
I can't go out now.

673
00:42:10,239 --> 00:42:11,679
Then I'll teach you some words.

674
00:42:13,039 --> 00:42:14,559
a b c d

675
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:16,400
d t n l

676
00:42:16,679 --> 00:42:17,679
g k h

677
00:42:24,960 --> 00:42:27,639
Mom, I'm full. I want to go watch cartoons.

678
00:42:27,639 --> 00:42:28,519
Go ahead.

679
00:42:30,079 --> 00:42:31,239
Let me wipe your mouth.

680
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:34,119
Go on.

681
00:42:54,159 --> 00:42:54,800
Ziqing

682
00:42:57,559 --> 00:42:59,239
I need to apologize to you.

683
00:43:00,960 --> 00:43:01,960
I'm sorry.
